{
  "text": "Mixed colloidal systems were prepared as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, T1107 and TPGS (weight ratio 1:3) were dispersed in distilled water at room temperature to get a final polymer concentration of 2% w/v. Samples were equilibrated at 25°C for 24 h before use.",
